input data to UAT server with standalone Splunk Enterprise
examine the data ingestion rate on the test index

Variable to consider to allocate disk space

- Daily rate of input
- Retention period (in days)
- Compression factor (~50% = 15% raw data + 35% for Splunk indexing)
- Padding (50 GB)

$Daily rate * Retention Period * Compression Factor + Padding = Total$
